These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, pakistani, malaysian, thai, polish, spanish
1. the thai is between the pakistani and the egyptian##2
2. the polish is on the right of the indian##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the polish is in the middle##1
5. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
6. the pakistani is on the left of the thai##1
7. the indian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | spanish | indian | polish | pakistani | thai | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, weightlifting, rugby, surfing, cycling, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Sport   | surfing | skateboarding | cycling | rowing | rugby | weightlifting | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  project-manager, lawyer, photographer, designer, coach, dancer, entrepreneur
1. the photographer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
2. the project-manager is on the left of the coach##1
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the coach is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
5. the designer is on the left of the project-manager##1
6. the project-manager is on the left of the coach##1
7. the photographer is in an even position##4
8. the project-manager is on the left of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Job   | lawyer | designer | project-manager | coach | entrepreneur | photographer | dancer |

