.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, climbing, water-polo, basketball, rugby, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | skiing | biathlon | water-polo | rugby | basketball | climbing | rowing |

