1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking milk##2
6. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite | hot-chocolate | milk | iced-tea | juice | almond-milk |

