.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
7 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, turtle, mouse, guinea-pig, bird, ferret
1. the owner of the mouse is the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Pet   | turtle | ferret | dog | guinea-pig | bird | hamster | mouse |

