1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Transport   | motorbike | airplane | ship | taxi | boat | bus | scooter |

